before I ever met you

14:57.200 --> 14:59.768
because the idea of you
lived in my heart.

14:59.811 --> 15:01.509
And I vow
the following...

15:03.685 --> 15:07.167
to love and cherish you...

15:07.210 --> 15:09.256
To stop leaving my
used ice cream bowls
in the sink...

15:09.299 --> 15:10.518
[CHUCKLES]

15:12.085 --> 15:14.435
And to not tune out
when you rant about

15:14.478 --> 15:16.089
what Ken did that day
at work.

15:18.961 --> 15:20.310
It's a different Ken.

15:20.354 --> 15:21.094
Oh.

15:23.792 --> 15:25.011
Clark.

15:26.447 --> 15:28.318
[CLEARS THROAT]

15:28.362 --> 15:29.406
Connor...

15:31.756 --> 15:34.281
Growing up
as a gay kid,

15:36.631 --> 15:39.677
I just never thought
this moment would be possible.

15:41.853 --> 15:43.072
But here we are.

15:44.987 --> 15:47.120
And though
this is a celebration,

15:48.512 --> 15:51.298
I can't help
but think of all the people

15:51.341 --> 15:54.779
who still have to be afraid
to just be who they are,

15:56.390 --> 15:57.695
to just love.

16:01.612 --> 16:02.657
And so...

16:04.093 --> 16:08.141
I vow that my love for you
will be so big

16:08.184 --> 16:10.099
that it will give us
the strength

16:10.143 --> 16:12.449
to never stop fighting
for what's right.

16:15.061 --> 16:19.413
Also, I vow that
every morning,

16:19.456 --> 16:23.069
when I get up,
hours and hours before you do,

16:23.112 --> 16:25.549
and see your used ice cream
bowl in the sink,

16:26.768 --> 16:28.291
not even soaking...

16:28.335 --> 16:29.553
[LAUGHTER]

16:32.730 --> 16:34.167
I will resent you.

16:35.646 --> 16:37.997
But I will rinse it
and put it in the dishwasher.

16:40.390 --> 16:42.088
We totally
wrote that part separately.

16:42.131 --> 16:43.350
[LAUGHTER]

16:44.525 --> 16:46.396
[LAUGHS]

16:46.440 --> 16:48.442
Um, so without further ado,

16:48.485 --> 16:51.227
by the power vested in me
by the course I took online,

16:51.271 --> 16:54.404
which I finished
in 26 minutes,

16:54.448 --> 16:59.453
I now pronounce you
loving husbands
and partners for life.

16:59.496 --> 17:01.498
You may kiss.

17:01.542 --> 17:03.109
[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]

17:04.588 --> 17:06.851
Ah! Yes!

