didn't plan anything,

17:31.528 --> 17:32.834
just the wedding.

17:32.877 --> 17:34.836
Well, we have a gift
that might change that.

17:34.879 --> 17:36.272
Oh, no, no.
We don't want any gifts.

17:36.316 --> 17:38.187
Well, let's hear them out.

17:38.231 --> 17:41.277
You're going to
Catalina Island, on us.

17:41.321 --> 17:42.800
[LAUGHS] You guys,
this is too much.

17:42.844 --> 17:44.846
I don't know
what to say.I do!

17:44.889 --> 17:46.195
