those wild buffalo

17:46.239 --> 17:48.241
my whole life.Oh, my God.

17:49.633 --> 17:51.374
Truly, thank you.

17:51.418 --> 17:54.682
Oh, Clarky,
you're so welcome,
and so are you.

17:54.725 --> 17:56.075
Oh! Oh.Mwah!

17:56.858 --> 17:57.946
Hey.

