just seemed less appealing.

18:16.965 --> 18:18.097
[LAUGHS]

18:19.141 --> 18:20.925
You always make me laugh.

18:20.969 --> 18:22.666
Yeah.

18:22.710 --> 18:25.104
[LAUGHS]Yeah, Damona.

18:25.147 --> 18:28.977
I'm aware that
what I'm about to declare

18:29.020 --> 18:31.414
could be
relationship dynamite.

18:31.458 --> 18:32.763
But as a man
who says what he feels...

18:32.807 --> 18:33.982
I love you.

18:34.722 --> 18:36.027
Ah.

18:37.159 --> 18:39.596
Yeah, I've never
been less irked

18:39.640 --> 18:40.989
to be beaten to the
punch before.

18:41.859 --> 18:43.818
Oh, and I love you.Okay.

