18:55.656 --> 18:56.744
Yep.

18:56.787 --> 18:58.311
We really did it.

18:59.312 --> 19:00.530
You're my husband.

19:00.574 --> 19:02.228
And always will be.

19:09.800 --> 19:12.107
You did an amazing job
up there.

19:12.151 --> 19:14.805
Thanks.
I meant every word,

19:14.849 --> 19:16.459
