19:52.060 --> 19:53.757
Hey.

19:53.801 --> 19:56.456
I'm so glad we got to see
Clark and Connor get married.

19:56.499 --> 19:59.676
And we got to do something
together as family,
just like you wanted.

19:59.720 --> 20:01.069
You're right.

20:01.112 --> 20:03.158
It was the perfect night.

20:03.202 --> 20:05.900
But it's not quite over.

20:05.943 --> 20:08.381
You know how you said
